1
00:00:26,119 --> 00:00:27,384
Hyung, should I cut this?

2
00:00:27,384 --> 00:00:32,645
Wash the strawberries first, then remove the stems and cut them in half.
No rush—take it slow.

3
00:00:32,645 --> 00:00:34,882
Okay.

4
00:00:43,079 --> 00:00:46,079
Ah…

5
00:00:48,399 --> 00:00:52,280
Let me see. Are you hurt badly?

6
00:00:52,600 --> 00:00:56,640
I’m fine. Just a small cut.

7
00:00:56,920 --> 00:01:00,640
Come here. Let’s put some medicine on it.

8
00:01:03,239 --> 00:01:04,813
Give me your hand.

9
00:01:05,820 --> 00:01:07,429
I’m really okay.

10
00:01:07,742 --> 00:01:09,281
Hurry.

11
00:01:12,960 --> 00:01:16,767
It stings, right?
Just hang in there.

12
00:01:20,320 --> 00:01:25,079
I shouldn’t have tried to act like I was good at it.

13
00:01:25,079 --> 00:01:26,655
It’s only because it’s your first time.

14
00:01:26,655 --> 00:01:30,533
I just…
wanted to do well in front of you.

15
00:01:30,801 --> 00:01:38,289
You’re doing great already.
Just don’t get hurt. That’s what matters most.

16
00:01:40,799 --> 00:01:42,756
Alright, we’re done.

17
00:01:43,517 --> 00:01:48,331
Okay, I’ll handle the fruit from here.
Yujin, help me fill the ice.

18
00:01:48,331 --> 00:01:50,380
Okay.

19
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:17,360
Yujin, the steam pitcher—careful. It’s hot.

20
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:54,800
So… the day finally comes where I’m having a drink
with our Yujin like this.

21
00:02:59,239 --> 00:03:02,442
Ah…
This feels strange.

22
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:04,336
Why?

23
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:09,302
I don’t know… it’s just—
time flew by so fast.

24
00:03:09,302 --> 00:03:14,005
I guess you still only remember me as a kid.

25
00:03:14,005 --> 00:03:19,892
No. I remember everything—
from back then, all the way to now.

26
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:26,400
And once the new semester starts, you’ll be busy,
so about the café—

27
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:28,207
you really don’t have to push yourself to work.

28
00:03:28,207 --> 00:03:31,648
I’m fine. I can do it.

29
00:03:32,230 --> 00:03:40,708
I know you want to help, and I appreciate that.
But take care of your own life first—school, studying, all of it.

30
00:03:41,133 --> 00:03:45,691
It just…
makes me uneasy, seeing you overdo it.

31
00:03:46,206 --> 00:03:47,489
Hyung…

32
00:03:48,094 --> 00:03:51,537
Why do you care so much about me?

33
00:03:51,537 --> 00:03:55,311
Why?
Because it’s you, Yujin.

34
00:03:57,437 --> 00:03:58,652
Slowly.

35
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:02,350
You don’t drink by downing it all at once.

36
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:06,940
I’m not drunk.

37
00:04:06,940 --> 00:04:13,755
Everyone says that—and none of them are sober.

38
00:04:34,320 --> 00:04:39,602
Yujin, no more.
I think you drank too fast.

39
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:47,624
I’m just…
so happy when I’m with you, hyung.

40
00:04:47,624 --> 00:04:49,256
Really happy.

41
00:04:50,375 --> 00:04:51,474
Yujin.

42
00:04:53,085 --> 00:04:54,567
Let’s drink some water.

43
00:04:55,417 --> 00:04:57,223
I’m not drunk.

44
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:07,820
Ah…
It really is three glasses.

45
00:05:19,039 --> 00:05:24,478
You’ve gotten so tall…
If you were going to be like this, you should’ve listened to me.

46
00:05:27,919 --> 00:05:29,707
Hyung?

47
00:05:29,707 --> 00:05:33,285
Yeah. I’m here. We’re home.

48
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:51,722
Yujin, wait a sec. Let’s take your clothes off.
You’ll be uncomfortable sleeping like this.

49
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:00,000
Hyung…

50
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:33,759
Yujin…

51
00:06:39,280 --> 00:06:43,619
Ah…
I’ve lost it, Lee Taeyoon.

52
00:07:17,400 --> 00:07:19,028
Mmm…

53
00:07:19,028 --> 00:07:22,386
You smell good, hyung…

54
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:26,210
Wait… where is this?

55
00:07:35,319 --> 00:07:39,599
Oh, I’m screwed.

56
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:56,632
You’re up.
Are you okay? Headache?

57
00:07:56,632 --> 00:07:59,418
Ah… yeah. I’m okay.

58
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:04,008
How did I get home last night?

59
00:08:08,159 --> 00:08:10,000
I carried you on my back.

60
00:08:11,843 --> 00:08:15,165
Sorry…
Was I heavy?

61
00:08:15,994 --> 00:08:19,724
No. You weren’t heavy at all.

62
00:08:21,879 --> 00:08:25,256
For now,
go wash up slowly.

63
00:08:27,639 --> 00:08:30,000
Then let’s have breakfast.

64
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:38,536
This is crazy…
I don’t remember anything.

65
00:08:40,719 --> 00:08:43,377
Yujin, I’ll leave some clothes by the door.

66
00:08:43,489 --> 00:08:45,000
Okay. Thanks.

67
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,514
Hyung…

68
00:08:50,431 --> 00:08:52,335
you’re too kind.

69
00:09:04,839 --> 00:09:06,874
Sit. It’s ready.

70
00:09:08,419 --> 00:09:13,328
Hyung, I don’t have to eat breakfast.
You didn’t have to go through all that.

71
00:09:13,328 --> 00:09:14,709
Seriously.

72
00:09:15,292 --> 00:09:19,627
You have to eat.
Come sit down.

73
00:09:24,160 --> 00:09:30,560
Start with the soup.
You drank on an empty stomach—that’s why you got drunk so fast.

74
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:32,963
I caused a lot of trouble last night, didn’t I?

75
00:09:32,963 --> 00:09:42,339
Not exactly trouble, but…
yeah. You and alcohol don’t mix.
If I’d known you were that lightweight,

76
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:45,151
I wouldn’t have let you drink.

77
00:09:46,651 --> 00:09:50,588
Once school starts, there’ll be drinking nights.
Try not to drink if you can.

78
00:09:50,588 --> 00:09:55,538
And if you do, only drink with someone you can trust.
Passing out like yesterday is dangerous.

79
00:09:55,829 --> 00:09:58,279
Okay. I get it.

80
00:09:59,532 --> 00:10:04,092
Did I…
do anything stupid last night?

81
00:10:07,640 --> 00:10:10,429
No. You fell asleep right away.

82
00:10:12,794 --> 00:10:14,454
I told you I’d take you home.

83
00:10:14,454 --> 00:10:16,114
Don’t argue. Come on.

84
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:20,440
I stole your bed, so you probably couldn’t even sleep properly…

85
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,644
Get some rest.

86
00:10:22,964 --> 00:10:27,164
Okay. Get home safe, Yujin.

87
00:11:08,623 --> 00:11:10,000
Ha…

88
00:11:10,233 --> 00:11:12,450
What the hell is that memory?

89
00:11:19,142 --> 00:11:22,485
I messed up before I even got to confess.
